        {
            "title": "美股重挫道指收跌878點  納指瀉3.56%  習特會或取消",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美股重演“四月暴跌”，美國總統特朗普稱對中國貨品加徵100%關稅，道瓊斯工業平均指數升283點後倒跌887點，波幅逾千點，納斯達克指數瀉逾3.5%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"美股3大指數跌近2%至近4%，在接近全日低位收市。資料圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1023x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251011_GL_US_market01_source_web_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"美股3大指數跌近2%至近4%，在接近全日低位收市。資料圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1023x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251011_GL_US_market01_source_web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">美股3大指數跌近2%至近4%，在接近全日低位收市。資料圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">特朗普在社交媒體表示，基於中國對稀土出口的限制，他沒有理由與中國國家主席習近平月底在南韓會面並威脅徵收新關稅，消息拖累美股周五先升後倒插，其後宣布對中國貨品加徵100%關稅。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"美股3大指數跌近2%至近4%，在接近全日低位收市。資料圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1023x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251011_GL_US_market01_source_web_.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"美股3大指數跌近2%至近4%，在接近全日低位收市。資料圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1023x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251011_GL_US_market01_source_web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">美股3大指數跌近2%至近4%，在接近全日低位收市。資料圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250430_GL_Amazon_source-ap_-2.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250430_GL_Amazon_source-ap_-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"英偉達(Nvidia) (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240606_FI_source-ap_Nvidia-1.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"英偉達(Nvidia) (AP圖片)\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240606_FI_source-ap_Nvidia-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">英偉達(Nvidia) (AP圖片)</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：蔚來官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250508_FI_source-web_09866-3-3.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：蔚來官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250508_FI_source-web_09866-3-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：蔚來官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"美股3大指數跌近2%至近4%，在接近全日低位收市。資料圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1023x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251011_GL_US_market01_source_web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">美股3大指數跌近2%至近4%，在接近全日低位收市。資料圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250430_GL_Amazon_source-ap_-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"英偉達(Nvidia) (AP圖片)\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240606_FI_source-ap_Nvidia-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">英偉達(Nvidia) (AP圖片)</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：蔚來官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250508_FI_source-web_09866-3-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：蔚來官網</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">道指高開36點後，最多升283點，之後曾倒跌887點，最低報45470點，收跌878點或1.9%，報45479點。兩個月來首次錄五連跌。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">標普500指數收挫2.71%，報6552點，以全日低位收市。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">納斯達克指數瀉3.56%，報22204點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">羅素2000指數收跌3.01%，報2394.595點，本周累跌3.29%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">費城半導體指數收跌6.32%，報6407點，本周累跌2.68%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">反映中國概念股表現的金龍指數跌6.1%，收報8018點，曾失守8000點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">本周累計，道指降低2.7%，標指滑落2.4%，納指倒退2.5%，羅素2000指數累跌3.29%，費城半導體指數本周累跌2.68%，羅素2000指數本周累跌3.29%。金龍中國指數急挫8.37%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250430_GL_Amazon_source-ap_-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250430_GL_Amazon_source-ap_-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅股中，特斯拉(Tesla)股價收市挫5.1%；亞馬遜急瀉5%，為跌幅最大道指成份股。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英偉達回落4.9%；英特爾推出新產品，股價漲4.9%後倒跌3.9% ; 高通(Qualcomm)的收購交易遭中國當局反壟斷調查，股價挫7.3%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">Meta收跌近3.9%；蘋果收跌3.45%；微軟收跌約2.2%；Alphabet收跌近2%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"英偉達(Nvidia) (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240606_FI_source-ap_Nvidia-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"英偉達(Nvidia) (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240606_FI_source-ap_Nvidia-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">英偉達(Nvidia) (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">牛仔褲品牌Levi's母公司Levi Strauss上調業績指引，但未達市場期望，股價插水12.6%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">費城半導體指數收跌6.32%，報6407點，本周累跌2.68%。AMD收跌7.7%，高通收跌7.3%，台積電美股跌6.4%，博通跌5.9%，美光科技跌約5.6%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中概股方面，文遠知行收跌約15%，蔚來跌約10%，小馬智行跌近9%，阿里、百度、小鵬汽車跌超8%，京東和騰訊粉單跌超6%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：蔚來官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250508_FI_source-web_09866-3-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：蔚來官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250508_FI_source-web_09866-3-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：蔚來官網</p>\n</a>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15335038-%e7%be%8e%e8%82%a1%e9%87%8d%e6%8c%ab%e9%81%93%e6%8c%87%e6%94%b6%e8%b7%8c878%e9%bb%9e-%e7%b4%8d%e6%8c%87%e7%80%893-56",
