        {
            "title": "金價重上4000美元關口　避險資金流入",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15334501&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">金價重上每盎司4000美元關口，在美國總統特朗普關稅威脅下，避險資金流入。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">現貨金收市報每盎司4017.34美元，升幅近1.1%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">紐約12月期金收報4000.4美元，升幅約0.7%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15334501-%e9%87%91%e5%83%b9%e9%87%8d%e4%b8%8a4000%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83%e9%97%9c%e5%8f%a3%e3%80%80%e9%81%bf%e9%9a%aa%e8%b3%87%e9%87%91%e6%b5%81%e5%85%a5-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20241016_CR_source-web_Gold_01.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-11 12:05:28",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美元美債息尾市跌幅擴大　特朗普稱對中國商品加徵關稅",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15334486&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美元及美債息尾市跌幅擴大，美國總統特朗普在紐約匯市尾市表示，下月起對中國商品加徵100%關稅，市場憂慮貿易戰或影響美國經濟。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"美國國債。\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2024/01/20240103_BLOG_-5.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"美國國債。\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2024/01/20240103_BLOG_-5.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">美國國債。</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美元指數低見98.808，最終報98.854，跌幅逾0.5%。本周累計升幅逾1%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">歐元和英鎊兌美元都升逾0.4%。美元兌日圓跌逾1%，報151.15日圓。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美債息亦下跌，指標10年期債息跌至4.04厘，跌逾10個基點。30年期債息跌至4.63厘附近，跌逾10個基點。2年期債息跌逾9個基點，在3.5厘左右。其後跌幅稍為回穩。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15334486-%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83%e7%be%8e%e5%82%b5%e6%81%af%e5%b0%be%e5%b8%82%e8%b7%8c%e5%b9%85%e6%93%b4%e5%a4%a7%e3%80%80%e7%89%b9%e6%9c%97%e6%99%ae%e7%a8%b1%e5%b0%8d%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e5%95%86%e5%93%81%e5%8a%a0",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/20240410_source-licensed_USD_FB.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-11 12:05:29",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "歐股收跌近1%或以上　憂慮新一輪貿易戰",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15334481&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">歐洲主要股市跌近1%或以上收市，因美國總統特朗普威脅要大規模增加中國進口商品關稅，引發新一輪貿易戰的憂慮。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"歐股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250410_FI_source-ap_Germany_Trump_Tariffs_25099406378758-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"歐股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250410_FI_source-ap_Germany_Trump_Tariffs_25099406378758-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">歐股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">泛歐指數Stoxx 600尾段急速轉跌，收市挫1.25%，報564點，</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">德國DAX指數收市報24241點，跌369點，跌幅1.5%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">法國CAC指數報7918點，跌123點，跌幅1.5%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英國富時100指數報9427點，跌81點，跌幅近0.9%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">總結全星期，德股累計跌近0.6%，英股跌近0.7%。法股跌2%，結束連續4星期升勢。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">意大利富時MIB指數收報42047點，下跌1.74%或744點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">西班牙IBEX 35指數收報15476點，走低0.69%或108點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15334481-%e6%ad%90%e8%82%a1%e6%94%b6%e8%b7%8c%e8%bf%911%e6%88%96%e4%bb%a5%e4%b8%8a%e3%80%80%e6%86%82%e6%85%ae%e6%96%b0%e4%b8%80%e8%bc%aa%e8%b2%bf%e6%98%93%e6%88%b0",
